snippet.title: Details of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's tumultuous marriage emerge
snippet.description:
Actor Johnny Depp is suing News Group Newspapers, publisher of The Sun, and the paper's executive editor, Dan Wootton, over an April 2018 article that called him a "wife-beater."

To read more: http://cbc.ca/1.5644717
